descriptionNullable:
This is a dataset of overall TV show ratings from all OTT platforms. It is extracted from [IMDb Website](https://www.imdb.com/) 

**This dataset contains seven columns that describe the television show, which are listed below:**
# Features

| Name         | Description |
| ----------- | ----------- |
|  id               |   Show id which is register by IMDb website                |
|  name         |   Name of the Show along with season if any                |
|  year           |   Year duration of the show which has start year and end year if any                |
|  certificate |   The certificates section records the ratings certificates given to titles within each country  |
|  runtime     |    Duration of Show              |
|  genre        |    Genre / Category of the Shows Belongs                |
|  ratings      |     IMDb rating given by all users               |

# Interactive

1. Tv Show Recommendation-based application
2. Create Dashboards using PowerBi/ Tableau or Other Analytics Tool
3. Create more datasets like Celebrities, Star or Director from this dataset
